256
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:28,050
Ms. Sheng, please. This is your room.

257
00:25:28,050 --> 00:25:31,170
Hot water is provided 24 hours at the hotel.

258
00:25:31,770 --> 00:25:36,420
This is your living room. We’ve arranged for someone to serve you one-on-one.

259
00:25:40,620 --> 00:25:42,680
Outside is the atrium garden.

260
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:45,480
Because of security reasons, Deputy Commander Xiao has ordered

261
00:25:45,480 --> 00:25:48,250
sealing all the windows of the hotel.

262
00:25:51,220 --> 00:25:53,220
This room is nice.

263
00:25:53,220 --> 00:25:55,930
But I have to call my husband first

264
00:25:55,930 --> 00:25:57,870
to ask him to send over my luggage.

265
00:25:57,870 --> 00:26:01,920
Don't worry, Ms. Sheng. Deputy Commander Xiao has arranged everything for you.

266
00:26:01,920 --> 00:26:03,730
Come on in.

267
00:26:25,420 --> 00:26:28,680
How is it? Is Ms. Sheng satisfied with my arrangements?

268
00:26:28,680 --> 00:26:31,660
Deputy Commander, that's very thoughtful of you.

269
00:26:31,660 --> 00:26:35,540
I was thinking about getting a few custom-fitted qipaos (Chinese dresses).

270
00:26:37,650 --> 00:26:39,150
Oh.

271
00:26:40,200 --> 00:26:45,820
I selected these pieces from the tailor shop that my wife used to have her custom-made outfits.

272
00:26:46,460 --> 00:26:51,030
I chose the colors and styles based on what she used to like.

273
00:26:51,030 --> 00:26:54,820
I'm relieved to know that you're happy with them.

274
00:26:55,770 --> 00:26:59,800
But I generally prefer western-style clothes. They are more comfortable.

275
00:26:59,800 --> 00:27:03,530
I didn't have much time, so I was only able to prepare these in a hurry.

276
00:27:03,530 --> 00:27:09,030
But I'll take down Ms. Sheng's preferences and ask them to prepare.

277
00:27:09,780 --> 00:27:12,840
Deputy Commander, how thoughtful and considerate of you.

278
00:27:12,840 --> 00:27:16,310
I'm doing this to make sure Ms. Sheng

279
00:27:16,310 --> 00:27:19,820
doesn't have to worry about the chores and can focus on her work.

280
00:27:19,820 --> 00:27:22,000
I hope that during the evaluation,

281
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:26,210
Ms. Sheng can complete and send all the evaluation reports to me.

282
00:27:26,820 --> 00:27:30,650
Of course, including today's report.

283
00:27:31,980 --> 00:27:35,320
Looks like I had better accept your request than respectfully decline.

284
00:27:35,320 --> 00:27:39,900
But, Deputy Commander, I have to call my husband and my child anyway,

285
00:27:39,900 --> 00:27:42,060
and explain what's happening.

286
00:27:42,060 --> 00:27:46,030
I've talked to Eldest Brother Shen about it, and he understands.

287
00:27:46,030 --> 00:27:49,620
And he supports our closed-session evaluation process.

288
00:27:49,620 --> 00:27:53,560
If there's anything you need, my room is right next to yours.

289
00:27:53,560 --> 00:27:55,540
I'm ready to help at any time.

290
00:27:56,700 --> 00:27:58,440
Thank you, Boss.

291
00:28:13,490 --> 00:28:18,810
Ms. Sheng, please have a good rest and let us know if you need anything.

292
00:28:18,810 --> 00:28:22,750
By the way, I like to drink some wine and listen to music before I go to sleep.

293
00:28:22,750 --> 00:28:25,160
Can you put a record player in my room?

294
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:28,830
Of course. You can also write down the names of your favorite records

295
00:28:28,830 --> 00:28:31,860
and we’ll bring them to your room along with the record player.

296
00:28:31,860 --> 00:28:33,670
Okay, thank you.

297
00:28:33,670 --> 00:28:35,320
You’re welcome.

298
00:28:46,390 --> 00:28:49,390
Commander, how did it go?

299
00:28:51,960 --> 00:28:54,240
In December, Zhang Xueliang

300
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:58,030
announced to change the flag. And in January,

301
00:28:58,530 --> 00:29:02,590
the Nanjing Government planned to reduce local military power.

302
00:29:02,590 --> 00:29:06,470
The forces of various factions were dissatisfied.

303
00:29:07,030 --> 00:29:10,780
Tell me, this idea of... unification.

304
00:29:10,780 --> 00:29:12,860
How much longer can we persist?

305
00:29:12,860 --> 00:29:14,650
Then, what does the governor say?

306
00:29:14,650 --> 00:29:17,270
Governor will definitely not agree with this.

307
00:29:17,900 --> 00:29:22,210
If this continues, there's going to be a war for sure.

308
00:29:22,210 --> 00:29:25,720
I can only do my best

309
00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:29,110
to make the Northern Territories and Nanjing co-exist while being different.

310
00:29:31,680 --> 00:29:35,410
Commander, no matter what path you choose,

311
00:29:35,410 --> 00:29:38,540
I'll follow you wherever you go.

312
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:55,860
We have to get the name list before that

313
00:29:55,860 --> 00:29:58,070
and deploy our operations against the Japanese.

314
00:29:58,070 --> 00:30:00,480
If we wait until they've made their presence, they'll become too big of a target.

315
00:30:00,480 --> 00:30:02,710
By then, it will be challenging for us to do anything.

316
00:30:05,010 --> 00:30:08,260
How can I get in touch with Eldest Brother Shen?

317
00:30:53,800 --> 00:30:55,640
Deputy Commander!

318
00:31:34,340 --> 00:31:36,280
[Bidding Document]

319
00:31:37,090 --> 00:31:42,090
Ms. Sheng, you came to my room so late at night.

320
00:31:42,090 --> 00:31:43,890
What is it that you're coming for?

321
00:31:55,420 --> 00:32:00,080
Ms. Sheng, are you blushing?

322
00:32:02,220 --> 00:32:05,880
Seems like Ms. Sheng is not like how others describe you.

323
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:08,680
You're not as open-minded as Western girls.

324
00:32:09,250 --> 00:32:13,470
Deputy Commander, you're way more open-minded than I thought.

325
00:32:18,470 --> 00:32:20,160
Oh?

326
00:32:28,040 --> 00:32:31,120
In fact, I would like to remind you, Deputy Commander.

327
00:32:31,120 --> 00:32:34,780
If someone takes a picture of what we’re doing right now,

328
00:32:34,780 --> 00:32:37,500
I’m afraid the headline of Beixin’s newspaper tomorrow will be

329
00:32:37,500 --> 00:32:39,680
the love affair between Deputy Commander Xiao and his female secretary

330
00:32:39,680 --> 00:32:42,670
during the Beixin Harbor evaluation period.

331
00:32:42,700 --> 00:32:48,000
We’re in Beixin. Nobody dares to do so yet.

332
00:32:48,070 --> 00:32:51,790
Or how about you try it out?

333
00:32:52,660 --> 00:32:55,780
Deputy Commander, you sure like to joke.

334
00:32:55,780 --> 00:33:01,150
I respect my marriage, and I respect my work even more.

335
00:33:01,150 --> 00:33:05,880
I’m just here to let Deputy Commander know that the typewriter you sent over isn’t working.

336
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:09,710
It’s an urgent task, so please send over a new one.

337
00:33:09,710 --> 00:33:13,680
Otherwise, I can’t promise to finish my work today.

338
00:33:13,680 --> 00:33:15,800
Of course.

339
00:33:17,770 --> 00:33:19,980
Rest assured, Ms. Sheng.

340
00:33:19,980 --> 00:33:22,140
I’ll ask someone to send it to you after I’m done with this.

341
00:33:22,140 --> 00:33:23,840
Thank you.

342
00:33:39,080 --> 00:33:42,150
[Huaxing Hotel]

343
00:33:42,150 --> 00:33:44,140
[Birdseye View of Beixin Harbor | Yamato Chamber of Commerce]

344
00:33:45,060 --> 00:33:49,510
The other designs have basically given up this section of the water.

345
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:52,680
The Yamato Chamber of Commerce's idea is to use the tiny space

346
00:33:52,680 --> 00:33:56,010
in between two mountains as the outfall,

347
00:33:56,010 --> 00:33:59,430
to shorten the route to North Korea.

348
00:33:59,430 --> 00:34:03,030
This location is also more concealed and windproof.

349
00:34:03,030 --> 00:34:06,900
Let's take another look at the east and west side.

350
00:34:06,900 --> 00:34:11,090
The benefit of this design is that

351
00:34:11,090 --> 00:34:14,440
the rocks on both sides act as natural wave breakers.

352
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:17,270
This can greatly reduce the construction cost.

353
00:34:24,140 --> 00:34:26,650
That's true.

354
00:34:27,700 --> 00:34:31,620
I have a different opinion from everyone.

355
00:34:31,620 --> 00:34:36,130
I'm not sure if you've considered the issue of the situation in the waterway.

356
00:34:37,980 --> 00:34:41,730
It's true that nobody mentioned this before.

357
00:34:41,730 --> 00:34:46,350
Right. It is a problem worth considering.

358
00:34:47,930 --> 00:34:51,990
[Birdseye View of Beixin Harbor | Yamato Chamber of Commerce]

359
00:34:51,990 --> 00:34:56,730
In Yamato Chamber of Commerce's proposal, they chose this section...

360
00:34:57,440 --> 00:35:00,350
to be the port area. I don't think that's a good idea.

361
00:35:00,350 --> 00:35:02,890
It has mountains and rocks on both sides,

362
00:35:02,890 --> 00:35:05,170
which can easily get loose due to weathering.

363
00:35:05,170 --> 00:35:10,740
If there is a landslide, it will cause safety problems.

364
00:35:10,740 --> 00:35:13,710
Even if it's not dangerous,

365
00:35:13,710 --> 00:35:15,990
the sand and stones will fall into the port.

366
00:35:15,990 --> 00:35:19,000
In the long term, they're definitely going to silt up.

367
00:35:19,900 --> 00:35:22,620
The waterway can be dredged if it's silted up.

368
00:35:22,620 --> 00:35:26,060
We can also reinforce the rocks and mountains to prevent them from loosening. Right?

369
00:35:26,060 --> 00:35:27,810
You're right.

370
00:35:32,900 --> 00:35:36,640
Even if the rocks and mountains get loose, we can just block them from falling with a net.

371
00:35:36,640 --> 00:35:40,930
Professor Wang, I don't think that's a good proposal.

372
00:35:40,930 --> 00:35:43,710
I don't agree with Professor Wang's proposal.

373
00:35:46,570 --> 00:35:47,890
What do you think?

374
00:35:47,890 --> 00:35:51,210
Look at this here, it's not appropriate indeed.

375
00:35:51,210 --> 00:35:54,840
- Look at this. This won't work.
- I still agree with this proposal.

376
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:58,900
Looks like the proposal of the Yamato Chamber of Commerce is quite controversial.

377
00:35:58,900 --> 00:36:01,330
Let's skip this for now and look at the next one.

378
00:36:32,670 --> 00:36:35,130
[Ellie's Bakery]

379
00:36:42,560 --> 00:36:46,280
Hey, Third Brother. I didn't get to ask you this morning.

380
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:50,130
Don't you think Sheng Hanjun's outfit today is quite familiar?

381
00:36:50,130 --> 00:36:52,390
She's dressed up like Third Sister-in-law, right?

382
00:36:52,390 --> 00:36:55,570
I mean, do you really have a brain?

383
00:36:55,570 --> 00:36:57,930
What's wrong about it?

384
00:37:03,860 --> 00:37:06,690
Here she comes.

385
00:37:07,400 --> 00:37:09,240
Hello!

386
00:37:13,520 --> 00:37:16,080
What's your topic of discussion today?

387
00:37:16,080 --> 00:37:18,240
Can I join you?

388
00:37:18,240 --> 00:37:21,190
Of course. We're honored to have a beautiful lady dining with us.

389
00:37:21,190 --> 00:37:22,840
Please.

390
00:37:30,770 --> 00:37:33,170
- Ma'am.
- Thank you.

391
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:45,810
What happened to your arm?

392
00:37:48,150 --> 00:37:50,950
Nothing serious. There's no sunshine in my room.

393
00:37:50,950 --> 00:37:54,710
And it's close to the garden, so I got eczema.

394
00:37:55,750 --> 00:37:58,110
I'll ask someone to bring some medicine to you.

395
00:37:58,110 --> 00:38:00,730
It's okay. The ointment doesn't work for me.

396
00:38:00,730 --> 00:38:04,480
I'll just go to the corridor and bathe in the sun.

397
00:38:06,330 --> 00:38:09,930
There's a room next to mine that faces the sun.

398
00:38:09,930 --> 00:38:11,720
You can move to that room.

399
00:38:11,720 --> 00:38:14,120
Thank you, Deputy Commander.

