00:39:28,970 --> 00:39:32,330
Mr. Sato, our people have been keeping a close eye on Huaxing Hotel.

405
00:39:32,330 --> 00:39:37,180
We found that Mo Weiyi secretly visited the Beixin Institute of Geology.

406
00:39:37,180 --> 00:39:40,130
Institute of Geology?

407
00:39:43,230 --> 00:39:46,810
- Why would he go there?
- He visited Gu Qiwen.

408
00:39:56,680 --> 00:40:00,280
Okay. Let's call it a day.

409
00:40:00,280 --> 00:40:01,940
Okay.

410
00:40:15,430 --> 00:40:17,450
You guys can go first.

411
00:40:23,050 --> 00:40:24,680
Let's go.

412
00:40:58,350 --> 00:41:02,810
Deputy Commander, what's going on?

413
00:41:03,610 --> 00:41:05,580
Nothing.

414
00:41:05,580 --> 00:41:07,670
I'm just here to tell you

415
00:41:07,670 --> 00:41:11,220
that we need two copies of the meeting minutes for tomorrow.

416
00:41:11,220 --> 00:41:13,810
Okay. No problem.

417
00:41:19,710 --> 00:41:21,370
The thunder is so loud. Aren't you scared?

418
00:41:21,370 --> 00:41:23,120
What's so scary about thunder?

419
00:41:23,120 --> 00:41:26,170
Deputy Commander, you're being too considerate.

420
00:41:29,790 --> 00:41:33,960
I found a few good wines in the wine cabinet. I'll charge them to your room.

421
00:41:34,770 --> 00:41:36,910
Do as you wish, Ms. Sheng.

422
00:41:36,910 --> 00:41:41,350
But we still have work tomorrow. Don't drink too much.

423
00:41:41,350 --> 00:41:43,060
No problem.

424
00:41:44,310 --> 00:41:46,200
Have a good rest.

425
00:41:46,200 --> 00:41:48,620
Good night, Deputy Commander.

